text: Sadia Gul (born 4 March 1998 in Bannu) is a Pakistani professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 91 in the world. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani female squash players Category:People from Bannu District Category:South Asian Games bronze medalists for Pakistan Category:South Asian Games medalists in squash
